    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is sound and drives smoothly, with all major systems functioning as expected. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only moderate wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It\u2019s a reliable, solid car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
